        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000032_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000032_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "But the same thing, with regard to the same, cannot be both the end and a means to the end.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000032_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000032_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore natural love and the love of choice cannot have the same object.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000033_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000033_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore the angel cannot love himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "But every movement tends towards something else.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "That is loved as a subsisting good, which is so loved that we wish well to it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000036_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000036_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "This kind of love has been called by the name \"concupiscence\" while the first is called \"friendship.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Consequently both angel and man naturally seek their own good and perfection.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000037_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000037_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "This is to love self.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000037_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000037_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Hence angel and man naturally love self, in so far as by natural appetite each desires what is good for self.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000037_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000037_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "On the other hand, each loves self with the love of choice, in so far as from choice he wishes for something which will benefit himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Dionysius used the terms \"uniting\" and \"binding\" in order to show the derivation of love from self to things outside self; as uniting is derived from unity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Whether an Angel Loves Another with Natural Love As He Loves Himself?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Objection one: It would seem that an angel does not love another with natural love as he loves himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "For love follows knowledge.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000043_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000043_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore it seems that one angel does not love another with natural love as he loves himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000044_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000044_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore one angel does not love another as himself, but loves himself more.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "But no angel is the end of another; and again, such love can be severed from him, as is the case with the demons, who have no love for the good angels.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000045_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000045_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore an angel does not love another with natural love as he loves himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000046_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000046_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore an angel naturally loves another as he loves himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000047_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000047_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Now what is one with a thing, is that thing itself: consequently every thing loves what is one with itself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000047_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000047_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "So, if this be one with it by natural union, it loves it with natural love; but if it be one with it by non natural union, then it loves it with non natural love.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000047_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000047_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Thus a man loves his fellow townsman with a social love, while he loves a blood relation with natural affection, in so far as he is one with him in the principle of natural generation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000048_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000048_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "And so everything loves another which is one with it in species, with a natural affection, in so far as it loves its own species.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "So then, it must be said that one angel loves another with natural affection, in so far as he is one with him in nature.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "But so far as an angel has something else in common with another angel, or differs from him in other respects, he does not love him with natural love.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000050_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000050_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "In another way the expression can qualify the knowledge and the love on the part of the knower and lover.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000050_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000050_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "And thus one angel does not know another as himself, because he knows himself by his essence, and the other not by the other's essence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000050_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000050_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "In like manner he does not love another as he loves himself, because he loves himself by his own will; but he does not love another by the other's will.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000051_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000051_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "For since natural affection rests upon natural unity, the angel naturally loves less what is less one with him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000051_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000051_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Consequently he loves more what is numerically one with himself, than what is one only generically or specifically.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000051_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000051_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "But it is natural for him to have a like love for another as for himself, in this respect, that as he loves self in wishing well to self, so he loves another in wishing well to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000052_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000052_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Nor can such natural love be stripped from the wicked angels, without their still retaining a natural affection towards the good angels, in so far as they share the same nature with them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000053_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000053_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "five]",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Whether an angel by natural love loves God more than he loves himself?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000055_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000055_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Now the Divine nature is far above the angelic nature.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000055_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000055_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore, according to natural love, the angel loves God less than self, or even than another angel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000056_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000056_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore the angel does not love God more than self with natural love.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000057_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000057_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "But nature's operation would not be self centered were it to tend towards anything else more than to nature itself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000057_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000057_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore the angel does not love God more than himself from natural love.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000058_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000058_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore the angels do not love God more than themselves by natural love.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000060_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000060_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "But the precept of loving God more than self is a moral precept of the law.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000060_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000060_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Therefore, it is of the law of nature. Consequently from natural love the angel loves God more than himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000061_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000061_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "But absolutely speaking, out of the natural love he loves himself more than he does God, because he naturally loves himself before God, and with greater intensity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000062_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000062_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "The falsity of such an opinion stands in evidence, if one but consider whither natural movement tends in the natural order of things; because the natural tendency of things devoid of reason shows the nature of the natural inclination residing in the will of an intellectual nature.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000062_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000062_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Now, in natural things, everything which, as such, naturally belongs to another, is principally, and more strongly inclined to that other to which it belongs, than towards itself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000062_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000062_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Such a natural tendency is evidenced from things which are moved according to nature: because \"according as a thing is moved naturally, it has an inborn aptitude to be thus moved,\" as stated in Phys.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000062_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000062_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "seventy eight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000062_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000062_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "And since reason copies nature, we find the same inclination among the social virtues; for it behooves the virtuous citizen to expose himself to the danger of death for the public weal of the state; and if man were a natural part of the city, then such inclination would be natural to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000063_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000063_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "Otherwise, if either of them loved self more than God, it would follow that natural love would be perverse, and that it would not be perfected but destroyed by charity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000066_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000066_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "And much more has everything a natural inclination towards what is the absolutely universal good.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6323_10337_000068_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6323/10337/6323_10337_000068_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6323",
        "content": "And because He is naturally loved by all so far as He is the universal good, it is impossible that whoever sees Him in His essence should not love Him. But such as do not behold His essence, know Him by some particular effects, which are sometimes opposed to their will.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
